

django下载及安装

https://www.djangoproject.com/download/


一、ubuntu上安装python的mysql驱动 MySQLDb出现的问题
http://sourceforge.net/projects/mysql-python/ 下载

1 ~/download/MySQL-python-1.2.3$ sudo python2.7 setup.py build
Traceback (most recent call last): File "setup.py", line 5, in from setuptools import setup, ExtensionImportError: No module named setuptools
解决：sudo apt-get install python-setuptools


2 EnvironmentError: mysql_config not found
解决：sudo apt-get install libmysqlclient-dev

3 pymemcompat.h:10:20: fatal error: Python.h: No such file or directorycompilation terminated.error: command 'gcc' failed with exit status 1
解决： sudo apt-get install python-dev 
